title: Transcriptome analysis of single cells from the mouse dentate gyrus [10X]
abstract: RNA sequencing was performed on 5454 single cells from dentate gyrus of CD-1 mice, sampled at postnatal day 12, 16, 24 and 35, with the aim of studying the postnatal dentate gyrus neurogenesis.
overall_design: 1129 single cells from postnatal day 12, 1440 from day 16, 1063 from day 24, and 1822 from day 35.
summary: RNA sequencing was performed on 5454 single cells from dentate gyrus of CD-1 mice, sampled at postnatal day 12, 16, 24 and 35, with the aim of studying the postnatal dentate gyrus neurogenesis.
